==历史==
[[Image:Cyark_Tikal_Temple_II.jpg|thumb]]
[[土木工程师|土木工程师]]本·凯希拉（[[美籍|美籍]][[伊拉克人|伊拉克人]]）于2003年创立了CyArk。20世纪90年代，凯希拉在第一个便携式[[三维扫描仪|三维扫描仪]]的发明和市场化中扮演了重要的角色。由Cyra科技生产的第一个扫描仪叫做{{link-en|Cyrax|Cyrax (HDS system)}}，最初设计就是用于调查等相关目的<ref name = "abate">{{Cite news
| last = Abate
| first = Tom
| title = Laser mapping tool traces ancient sites - Device made for contractors helps archaeologists create first-ever digital blueprints
| work = SFGate - Innovations
| accessdate = 2014-10-11
| date = 2007-07-22
| url = http://www.sfgate.com/business/article/INNOVATIONS-Laser-mapping-tool-traces-ancient-2579950.php
| language = en
| archive-date = 2014-10-17
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141017195711/http://www.sfgate.com/business/article/INNOVATIONS-Laser-mapping-tool-traces-ancient-2579950.php
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。

2001年，Cyra科技及其所有发明专利被卖给了瑞士的[[徕卡测量系统|徕卡测量系统]]<ref>{{Cite web
| title = History
| work = Leica Geosystems
| accessdate = 2014-10-11
| url = http://www.leica-geosystems.com/en/History_834.htm
| language = en
| archive-date = 2014-10-18
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141018124349/http://www.leica-geosystems.com/en/History_834.htm
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。

在Cyra科技被出售之后，本·凯希拉开始专注于使用激光扫描技术来记录历史和文化遗产，并创立了CyArk<ref name = "eapowell">{{Cite news
| volume = Volume 62
| issue = No 3
| last = Powell
| first = Eric A
| title = The Past in High-Def
| work = Archaeology Magazine
| accessdate = 2014-10-11
| date = May–June 2009
| url = http://archive.archaeology.org/0905/etc/high_def.html
| language = en
| archive-date = 2014-07-18
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140718135410/http://archive.archaeology.org/0905/etc/high_def.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。

CyArk的推广最初主要围绕凯希拉的出生地--伊拉克。在伊拉克战争期间，伊拉克大量的文化遗产遭到掠夺。一些历史遗迹例如[[巴比伦|巴比伦]]和[[萨迈拉|萨迈拉]]遭到了军事打击。此外，作为CyArk公众形象的凯希拉多次在一些大会上发表演讲。他于2008年参加了谷歌举办的Zeitgeist大会，2011年又参加了[[TED大会|TED大会]]，并在其中发表了演讲。他在演讲中讲述自己的人生以及利用数字手段保护“人类记忆”的可能性。不过在此后几年，由于CyArk已经获得了可观的关注度，本·凯希拉更多的扮演顾问的角色。

==CyArk 500==
2013年10月，CyArk发起了CyArk 500挑战"。 该机构宣布它试图在接下来的5年内扫描500个历史遗迹<ref name = "cyark2014">{{Cite web
| title = CyArk 500 Annual Summit 2014
| language = en
| work = Digital meets Culture
| accessdate = 2014-10-09
| date = 2014-10-07
| url = http://www.digitalmeetsculture.net/article/cyark-500-annual-summit-2014/
| archive-date = 2014-10-01
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141001040856/http://www.digitalmeetsculture.net/article/cyark-500-annual-summit-2014/
